{"tid":857430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俏皮唱中國國歌遭舉報 直播主被封殺","createTime":"2018-10-11T05:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T13:27:55.000Z","uid":66943,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0dcd4eb6b8de180aaf0ef717e23848c4eb06bf94","tid":857430,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:45:57.000Z","msg":"大陸中心／綜合報導【 10/11 11:18 發稿 ｜ 12:25 更新：新增影音 】<br />\n<br />\n大陸人氣直播主莉哥（楊凱莉）擁有百萬粉絲，她日前在直播時，改編中國國歌，以俏皮的方式演唱，引爆大陸網友怒火，莉哥馬上遭到舉報，直播帳號也立刻被封。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4LKONlosqFM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4LKONlosqFM&d=WXCoeIKiCYKcGhUo7hujo9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=3704195a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4LKONlosqFM</a><br />\n<br />\n▲直播主莉哥改編中國國歌。<br />\n<br />\n據《人民網》報導，莉哥在十一長假期間開直播，用自己改編的曲調，唱了中國國歌「起來，不願做奴隸的人們」，還一邊手舞足蹈，但這個舉動惹怒大陸網友，舉報她對國歌不敬，公然竄改國歌曲譜。大陸《國歌法》規定，奏唱《義勇軍進行曲》，應當按照原本的歌詞和曲譜，不得以有損歌曲尊嚴的形式奏唱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RBR0W37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRBR0W37.jpg&h=755c2bc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲莉哥遭全面封殺，發表聲明道歉。（圖／翻攝自新浪）<br />\n<br />\n莉哥被大批網友砲轟「腦殘」、「活該」，她在網路平台「虎牙」所有的直播間和帳號，遭到全面封殺，相關影像也全面下架，「虎牙」昨（10）日針對此事發表聲明，<span style=\"color: red;\">表示會對她進行整改教育</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n莉哥也發表聲明道歉，「我從未想過對國歌不敬，但作法卻背道而馳，國歌是肅穆的，不應該在直播間裏唱，是我思想覺悟不高，對《中華人民共和國國歌法》認識不深，才會造成這樣的錯誤。我將停止一切直播工作，進行自我整改，痛定思痛、<span style=\"color: red;\">深刻反思並全面接受思想政治和愛國主義教育</span>。」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n的去集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46bc6011520f5d9355a0602f7ffb58c8becc209d","tid":857430,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bfc88dc6d734f229959acdfe482e41a5c75f32","tid":857430,"uid":86383,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"抵死，擺佢入集中營<br />\n屌到佢塊閪變牛肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de5bdce8bce8d2a6e239bb7364485d199956564","tid":857430,"uid":91833,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:28:53.000Z","msg":"真心我覺得佢唔靚，好恐怖，唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2904cb5f51174303c0b424bee493b84c3691bc","tid":857430,"uid":86383,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:28:31.000Z","msg":"話時話，佢今年貴庚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁似啲4X歲化厚妝扮妹妹仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa881207cd49553f67b1c3d7d9b67a83a88a378","tid":857430,"uid":193364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7aa01820d531c5aa8eaf6ae1747b79ffc6d884","tid":857430,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7bfc88dc6d734f229959acdfe482e41a5c75f32","tid":857430,"uid":86383,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"抵死，擺佢入集中營<br />\n屌到佢塊閪變牛肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:32:24.000Z","msg":"原本都係牛肺"},{"pid":"a97d2c34268a788f7165160d84c78ca09368eb35","tid":857430,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a819fa4586a9823758de0aa7e74ab34b97004672","tid":857430,"uid":102078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:27:55.000Z","msg":"抖音造就呢位網紅"}]}